						               													<description>Work together to race around the mysterious island and find the hidden treasure before the big storm covers the island! The treasure hunters have found a treasure map for the mysterious island and have arrived to find the hidden treasure. Players must work together to explore the different areas of the island to find all the treasure before they leave.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In My First Treasure Hunt kids race around the island, trying to collect all the hidden treasure while outrunning the big storm. Players will move across the board using their numbered cards to collect their treasure tokens while avoiding obstacles that will set them back. Work as a team to explore all the areas of the island in time to find the treasure.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Storm cards are mixed into the deck of cards players use to move around the board. When a storm card is picked up and played, a new storm cloud token is added to the top of the board. if all the storm cloud spaces are filled with cloud tokens before players find all the treasure and get back to their canoe, then the game is lost.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If the treasure hunters find all their treasure and make it back to their canoe before the storm covers the island, everyone wins!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;My First Treasure Hunt uses creative and colorful scenes that make searching for treasure fun and imaginative. This cooperative game is a perfect introduction to basic counting, teamwork, and strategic thinking.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
